  <scopecontent id="aspace_20415ad0341e8830457c453d10e0d243">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The collection contains several letters to Joseph, including one from Daniel De Leon, several unpublished manuscripts, including "The Discovery of Neptune, and an untitled ms. about the Paris Exhibition of 1900 and the socialist movement in Europe (principally in France and Germany), clippings, and biographical information.</p>  </scopecontent>
